author: The Irish Times
title: Coronavirus: China denies allegations pandemic began in lab near Wuhan
description: ‘There is no fast track back to normal’, says WHO director as global cases pass 2 million
content:
China is refuting allegations that the coronavirus pandemic may have originated in a laboratory near the city of Wuhan where contagious samples were being stored.
